<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="3Apr1933"><font color="red">3 April 1933</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): Would you also kindly add &hellip; that the type they have chosen for the Transition fragment as published is entirely different from the one in the first proofs (a copy of which I sent to you or to Mr Morley) and has met with a chorus of universal disapproval as being too blurred and difficult to decipher. </div>
